{# FAQ — GEO-optimised Q&A format #}
<section class="section section---bg-light">
  <div class="section__inner--narrow">
    <p class="section__label">FAQ</p>
    <h2 class="section__title">Everything you need to know</h2>

    <div role="list">
      <div class="faq__item" role="listitem">
        <button class="faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
          What is Duo Input technology?
        </button>
        <div class="faq__answer">
          Duo Input is a patented technology (Swedish Patent Office PRV, application
          no. 2030154-5, classification G06F3/0488 — "Apparatus and Method for Supporting
          Touch Input Events") that allows the advisor or cashier and the customer to
          interact on the same screen simultaneously without technical conflicts. It applies
          across banking, retail, and hotel settings.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq__item" role="listitem">
        <button class="faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
          Do we need to change our existing system?
        </button>
        <div class="faq__answer">
          No. ID24 integrates seamlessly with existing POS systems, banking business
          systems, and hotel property management systems (PMS) without any modifications.
          The software runs on a separate device and communicates passively with your
          existing setup.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq__item" role="listitem">
        <button class="faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
          How long does it take to launch a pilot?
        </button>
        <div class="faq__answer">
          A pilot typically goes live within 8–12 weeks from sign-off. ID24 handles remote
          installation, software testing, and customization with full support included — no
          internal IT effort required on your side.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq__item" role="listitem">
        <button class="faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
          Which industries does ID24 serve?
        </button>
        <div class="faq__answer">
          Primarily retail, banking, and hotels. With 15+ years of experience and software
          installed in 20+ countries, ID24 is now bringing the same proven three-pillar
          methodology (Data Collection, Gamification, Execution) into the financial services
          sector with a dedicated banking solution.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq__item" role="listitem">
        <button class="faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
          How does the cashier fraud detection AI work?
        </button>
        <div class="faq__answer">
          The AI anonymously analyzes transaction data — discounts, returns, error
          registrations, and cashier activity patterns — against industry benchmarks and
          custom algorithms. Store managers receive actionable insights in real time or
          via weekly reports.
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq__item" role="listitem">
        <button class="faq__question" aria-expanded="false">
          What hardware is compatible with ID24?
        </button>
        <div class="faq__answer">
          Any consumer-grade Android, iOS, or Windows tablet works with ID24's software.
          Purpose-built options include the D|2 range with integrated NFC and camera in
          8", 10", 13.3", and 15.6" sizes. The Adyen SFO1 8" (Android with NFC),
          Wacom DTU-1141B 10", and Wacom DTC141W0 14" displays are also supported.
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>